    <briefdescription>
<para>Base object for data and behavior attached to a <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> trait slot. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1TraitObject" kindref="compound">TraitObject</ref> provides lifecycle hooks for View-owned on-demand extensions. It is a BaseObject so public trait handles can keep the usual DALi handle/body shape while <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> stores only objects that explicitly opt into trait semantics. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
